reviewText: What can I say...of course I like it.  I am a diehard STL fan
Being a big baseball fan, I give this video 5 stars. I was particularly interested in the only All-St. Louis World Series of 1944. Thanks. Dick Burnon
Great historical DVD for any Cardinal fan.

My Grandfather was in the 1944 World Series with the Browns and I knew this would be a perfect gift for my Father who talks fondly of it.  Sadly, I never did see him in the video, but otherwise, it was a decent coverage of the game.  The way it's shown is more like highlights than an actual video of the full game.

My brother and I absolutely enjoyed watching this DVD and we continue to watch it over and over.  Thank you.

We loved it!!
Great vintage baseball footage narrated by original announcers. Not too long and drawn out. Fun to see the footage of Cardinal fans, at the time, also.
I bought this video for my husband who is a HUGE St. Louis Cardinals fan.  We enjoyed watching it, not only for the baseball highlights, but also for the historical references.  Great video!!
